creator: Radix Software Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml: OfficeMaps is an easy to use web based visual staff directory with office floor plans.  Make hot desking easy for staff using the OfficeMaps touch screen kiosk.  Staff can also use this OfficeMaps Mobile app to find people, check-in and check-out of desks. A subscription to OfficeMaps must be purchased separately before OfficeMaps Mobile can be used.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Changes to application security. All saved configuration will need to be re-entered.
Instance code, saved login details and API URL.
If Instance is located in US - https://api-us.officemaps.com and UK, https://api-uk.officemaps.com.
New basic Map view tab, display Assets and People allocated to a Site Level.
